# Configuration file for AI Video Generator
# Add your free API keys here

# Google Gemini API Key (Free tier: 60 requests per minute)
# Get it from: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# Optional: Unsplash API Key (Free tier: 50 requests per hour)
# Get it from: https://unsplash.com/developers
UNSPLASH_ACCESS_KEY=your_unsplash_access_key_here

# Optional: Pexels API Key (Free tier: 200 requests per hour)
# Get it from: https://www.pexels.com/api/
PEXELS_API_KEY=your_pexels_api_key_here

# Optional: Pixabay API Key (Free tier: 100 requests per hour) 
# Get it from: https://pixabay.com/api/docs/
PIXABAY_API_KEY=your_pixabay_api_key_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Replace the values above with your actual API keys
# 2. Only Gemini is needed for basic functionality
# 3. Other APIs are optional for better stock images
# 4. All APIs mentioned are completely FREE with generous limits
